<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 18:10:38 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“可憎”：希伯来大学校长猛烈抨击全国学生会推动的法案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/abomination-hebrew-university-president-slams-bill-pushed-by-national-student-union/00000190-2705-d14b-a999-27ed677c0000</link><description>该法案将迫使大学立即解雇任何发表被认为否定以色列作为犹太民主国家存在的观点的教员</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 17:38:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/abomination-hebrew-university-president-slams-bill-pushed-by-national-student-union/00000190-2705-d14b-a999-27ed677c0000</guid></item><item><title>一个依良心拒服兵役者对以色列人和巴勒斯坦人从河流到海洋的生活的愿景</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-refusniks-vision-of-life-for-israelis-and-palestinians-from-the-river-to-the-sea/00000190-2688-d14b-a999-27e9f5770000</link><description>索菲亚·奥尔 (Sofia Orr) 因拒绝加入以色列国防军而刚刚在军事监狱里度过了 85 天。这位 19 岁的女孩在被认定为良心拒服兵役者后获释，她讲述了自己这样做的原因、左翼和右翼极端分子的袭击，以及她从狱友那里听到的消息</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 17:33:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/a-refusniks-vision-of-life-for-israelis-and-palestinians-from-the-river-to-the-sea/00000190-2688-d14b-a999-27e9f5770000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡随身携带一本关于古希腊民主衰落的书。我们应该读多少内容？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-carries-book-on-the-fall-of-greek-democracy-how-much-should-we-read-into-it/00000190-25f4-de0a-af9b-fdffa92d0000</link><description>最近几天，内塔尼亚胡一定要在《雅典的兴衰》中拍照，该片聚焦于雅典领导人中普遍存在的道德败坏，并导致了雅典的垮台。内塔尼亚胡很可能不会内化这些教训</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 17:29:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/netanyahu-carries-book-on-the-fall-of-greek-democracy-how-much-should-we-read-into-it/00000190-25f4-de0a-af9b-fdffa92d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 255 天：消息人士称，如果没有“后天”计划，以色列国防军在拉法取得的成果就被浪费了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-255-idf-gains-in-rafah-wasted-without-day-after-plan-source-says/00000190-2702-d14b-a999-27eb76150000</link><description>甘茨辞职后，内塔尼亚胡总理解散战争内阁 ■ 接近内塔尼亚胡的消息人士表示，有关战争的敏感决定仍将在排除极右翼部长的有限论坛上做出 ■ 拜登的中东特使阿莫斯·霍赫斯坦在前往黎巴嫩之前在以色列与以色列高级官员会面试图缓和以色列和真主党之间的紧张局势 ■ 这是战争进入 255 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 16:37:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-255-idf-gains-in-rafah-wasted-without-day-after-plan-source-says/00000190-2702-d14b-a999-27eb76150000</guid></item><item><title>联合国小组称缺乏数据来确定加沙北部是否存在饥荒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/un-panel-says-data-lacking-to-determine-whether-famine-exists-in-northern-gaza/00000190-269a-d2de-af9e-67fa68040000</link><description>联合国专家小组反驳了人权组织的调查结果，但警告不要利用该报告来否认“加沙地带目前无疑正在遭受极端的人类苦难”</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:46:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/un-panel-says-data-lacking-to-determine-whether-famine-exists-in-northern-gaza/00000190-269a-d2de-af9e-67fa68040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列面临着相信与真主党的战争不可避免的危险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/could-this-talmudic-concept-help-avert-an-inevitable-israel-hezbollah-war/00000190-25da-d95e-a3ff-edfe95270000</link><description>你知道 ipcha Mistabra 是什么吗？你应该——以色列的军事和政治领导人现在就应该考虑黎巴嫩可能爆发的全面战争</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/could-this-talmudic-concept-help-avert-an-inevitable-israel-hezbollah-war/00000190-25da-d95e-a3ff-edfe95270000</guid></item><item><title>马尔代夫正在审查因排除巴勒斯坦人问题而全面禁止以色列人的提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/maldives-reviewing-proposed-blanket-ban-on-israelis-over-issue-of-palestinians-exclusion/00000190-2673-d5f5-a5d6-effb15270000</link><description>司法部长艾哈迈德·乌沙姆表示，该禁令也将影响持有以色列护照的巴勒斯坦人，这是“一些人非常关心的问题”</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 15:37:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/asia-and-australia/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/maldives-reviewing-proposed-blanket-ban-on-israelis-over-issue-of-palestinians-exclusion/00000190-2673-d5f5-a5d6-effb15270000</guid></item><item><title>极端正统派部长关于军队豁免：“我们赢得了选举，难道我们不能做出决定吗？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-minister-on-idf-exemption-we-won-the-election-dont-we-get-to-decide/00000190-2518-d3e6-a191-773bcbb90000</link><description>建设和住房部长声称国防机构对征召极端正统犹太人不感兴趣；以色列国防军司令哈勒维：征召正统派显然是必要的，每个营都将减轻数千名预备役人员的负担</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 14:31:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/ultra-orthodox-minister-on-idf-exemption-we-won-the-election-dont-we-get-to-decide/00000190-2518-d3e6-a191-773bcbb90000</guid></item><item><title>作为阿拉伯以色列人在朝觐期间访问麦加，我的身份让加沙最大的支持者感到困惑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/visiting-mecca-as-a-palestinian-israeli-my-identity-confused-gazas-biggest-supporters/00000190-25cc-d2de-af9e-65ee12ef0000</link><description>陪同朝觐者前往麦加朝觐的《国土报》记者 Deiaa Haj Yahia 会见了一些信徒，他们不知道以色列有穆斯林阿拉伯公民，其他人则谴责“犹太复国主义政权”，与加沙巴勒斯坦人和担心与以色列关系正常化的沙特人深表声援。以色列可能“损害我们在穆斯林世界的地位”</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 13:21:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/visiting-mecca-as-a-palestinian-israeli-my-identity-confused-gazas-biggest-supporters/00000190-25cc-d2de-af9e-65ee12ef0000</guid></item><item><title>2023年以色列国防出口额达到创纪录的131亿美元；超过三分之一是防空交易</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/israel-defense-exports-hit-record-13-billion-in-2023-over-a-third-are-air-defense-deals/00000190-25d7-d5f5-a5d6-edffd8630000</link><description>报告称，近五年来，以色列国防出口规模翻了一番，近三年出口额记录每年都被打破</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 12:41:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/israel-defense-exports-hit-record-13-billion-in-2023-over-a-third-are-air-defense-deals/00000190-25d7-d5f5-a5d6-edffd8630000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨辞职后内塔尼亚胡解散以色列战时内阁，本格维尔要求纳入</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dissolves-war-cabinet-after-gantz-exit-ben-gvir-demands-for-inclusion/00000190-25b6-d2de-af9e-65f6ad120000</link><description>一位政治消息人士称，解散内阁严格来说是声明性的，旨在防止极右翼部长参与敏感决策；战时内阁最初是在中间派议员甘茨和艾森科特于十月加入内塔尼亚胡战时政府时组建的</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 11:06:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-dissolves-war-cabinet-after-gantz-exit-ben-gvir-demands-for-inclusion/00000190-25b6-d2de-af9e-65f6ad120000</guid></item><item><title>亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡支持以色列国防军10月7日的“背叛”阴谋，指责以色列最高法院“掩盖事实”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/yair-netanyahu-bolsters-idf-oct-7-betrayal-conspiracy-accuses-top-court-of-cover-up/00000190-2548-df6a-a3f6-2f5810440000</link><description>10 月 7 日，以色列总理之子猛烈抨击了高等法院暂停国家监察机构对军队行动调查的决定，并暗示法院希望成立一个“左翼掩盖委员会”</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 09:26:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/yair-netanyahu-bolsters-idf-oct-7-betrayal-conspiracy-accuses-top-court-of-cover-up/00000190-2548-df6a-a3f6-2f5810440000</guid></item><item><title>拜登高级特使访问该地区，白宫试图阻止以色列与真主党全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-special-envoy-to-visit-israel-in-bid-to-prevent-lebanon-escalation/00000190-2237-d4b4-a7d6-eaf791520000</link><description>尽管拜登政府在霍赫斯坦的会谈中表达了紧迫性，但高级官员承认，加沙战争的结束和人质的释放是在以色列和黎巴嫩边境达成协议的必要条件</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/u-s-special-envoy-to-visit-israel-in-bid-to-prevent-lebanon-escalation/00000190-2237-d4b4-a7d6-eaf791520000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：真主党高级成员在黎巴嫩南部袭击车辆时被暗杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-live/israeli-military-says-hezbollah-bringing-us-to-brink-of-escalation/00000190-2411-df11-a3b9-a5174e600000</link><description>以色列军方发言人称真主党“将我们带到了升级的边缘” ■ 以色列国防军表示，在以色列北部阿卡附近拦截了来自黎巴嫩的空中目标 ■ 以色列国防军宣布每日“战术暂停”，试图增加对加沙的援助流量 ■ 反对政府封锁的抗议者以色列的主要高速公路</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:53:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article-live/israeli-military-says-hezbollah-bringing-us-to-brink-of-escalation/00000190-2411-df11-a3b9-a5174e600000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方非法拘留11名反政府抗议者近一天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-unlawfully-holds-11-anti-government-protesters-in-custody-for-nearly-a-day/00000190-22c3-d3e6-a191-76ebac3b0000</link><description>周日早上，警方提出了限制释放抗议者的请求，但到下午，只有三人按照法律要求被带去参加第一次保释听证会。被捕并随后被释放的人包括《国土报》摄影师伊泰·罗恩 (Itai Ron)</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 21:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-unlawfully-holds-11-anti-government-protesters-in-custody-for-nearly-a-day/00000190-22c3-d3e6-a191-76ebac3b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列联盟重新提出有争议的法案，赋予政府对城市拉比任命的权力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/coalition-re-introduces-contentious-bill-giving-govt-power-over-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-21d1-d880-a7f5-b5d5d7340000</link><description>由于联盟成员之间存在分歧，该法案的讨论于三月份暂停，随后将恢复讨论。该法案还允许政府任命并资助约 600 名新拉比</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/coalition-re-introduces-contentious-bill-giving-govt-power-over-city-rabbi-appointments/00000190-21d1-d880-a7f5-b5d5d7340000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院规定，父亲在出生后皈依基督教的孩子可能会获得以色列公民身份</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/children-whose-fathers-converted-after-birth-may-get-israeli-citizenship-top-court-rules/00000190-2250-d3e6-a191-767bc21e0000</link><description>Ronnen 和 Vogelman 法官表示，授予身份符合《公民法》保护家庭单位和确保儿童福利的客观目的</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/children-whose-fathers-converted-after-birth-may-get-israeli-citizenship-top-court-rules/00000190-2250-d3e6-a191-767bc21e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反政府组织向内塔尼亚胡联盟发起“抵抗周”，要求达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-anti-government-groups-call-for-week-of-resistance-in-joint-press-conference/00000190-21d5-d4b4-a7d6-e9f7ed320000</link><description>经过动荡的一周后，三个抗议团体正在为为期一周的全国性抗议和封锁做准备，呼吁所有以色列人立即加入他们的选举要求</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:25:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/israeli-anti-government-groups-call-for-week-of-resistance-in-joint-press-conference/00000190-21d5-d4b4-a7d6-e9f7ed320000</guid></item><item><title>定居者在西岸袭击巴勒斯坦牧羊人和以色列活动人士</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/settlers-assault-palestinian-shepherds-israeli-activists-in-west-bank/00000190-2235-df11-a3b9-a337fabe0000</link><description>活动人士称，定居者曾两次殴打他们以及他们正在帮助的牧羊人，并向他们投掷石块</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 19:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/settlers-assault-palestinian-shepherds-israeli-activists-in-west-bank/00000190-2235-df11-a3b9-a337fabe0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列议会小组推动将预备役军人豁免年龄延长一年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-advances-move-to-extend-raising-exemption-age-for-reservists-by-a-year/00000190-2234-d880-a7f5-b6f4507b0000</link><description>规范该措施的紧急命令将于六月底到期，即生效四个月后。如果议会通过该提案，士兵将在预备役服役至41岁，军官将服役至46岁，担任关键职务的预备役人员将服役至50岁</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 18:57:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-16/ty-article/.premium/knesset-panel-advances-move-to-extend-raising-exemption-age-for-reservists-by-a-year/00000190-2234-d880-a7f5-b6f4507b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>